column2: SELECT top # sp.ra, sp.dec, sp.z, sp.class, sp.subclass, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS mag_u, sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS mag_g, sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS mag_r, sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS mag_i, sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS mag_z, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4, f.peak, f.integr, f.rms FROM PhotoObj AS sp LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = sp.objid JOIN PhotoZ as pz ON pz.objid = sp.objid WHERE (sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u > #) AND (sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g > #) AND (sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > #) AND (sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i > #) AND (sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z > #) into myDB.test
